  "texts": [
    "Many AI applications in this domain, such as neural decoding of consumer preferences or AI-based taste reconstruction, involve complex processes that are difficult for the general public to grasp.",
    "Without clear and accessible explanations, consumers may feel excluded from decision-making or develop mistrust toward the technologies embedded in their daily lives.",
    "To prevent this, developers and companies should invest in consumer education ini-tiatives.",
    "These efforts should explain how AI systems operate, what types of data they rely on, and what potential benefits or risks they carry.",
    "Transparency should also be reflected in product labeling, marketing strategies, and user interfaces."
  ],
